<h1>Problem 957 - 2014 IMOSL, A5</h1>
<h2 class='difficulty'>Difficulty: 9</h2>
<p>Consider all polynomials \(P(x)\) with real coefficients that have the following property: for any two real numbers \(x\) and \(y\) one has\[|y^2-P(x)|\le 2|x|\quad\text{if and only if}\quad |x^2-P(y)|\le 2|y|.\]Determine all possible values of \(P(0)\).</p>
